[2;36m│[0m Great findings:                                                                                                                                                                       [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m - Backticks ``` ` ``` are ALLOWED                                                                                                                                                     [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m - Forward slash `/` is ALLOWED                                                                                                                                                        [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m - `alert` (lowercase) is ALLOWED                                                                                                                                                      [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m - Uppercase `S` is BLOCKED                                                                                                                                                            [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m - Square brackets `[` and `]` are BLOCKED                                                                                                                                             [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m                                                                                                                                                                                       [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m So the filter blocks:                                                                                                                                                                 [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m - Single quotes `'`                                                                                                                                                                   [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m - Uppercase letters (at least some: A, S)                                                                                                                                             [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m - `<` and `>`                                                                                                                                                                         [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m - Square brackets `[` and `]`                                                                                                                                                         [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m                                                                                                                                                                                       [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m And ALLOWS:                                                                                                                                                                           [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m - Lowercase letters (a-z)                                                                                                                                                             [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m - Double quotes `"`                                                                                                                                                                   [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m - Backticks ``` ` ```                                                                                                                                                                 [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m - Parentheses `(` and `)`                                                                                                                                                             [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m - Operators: `+`, `=`, `.`, `/`                                                                                                                                                       [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m - Semicolon `;`                                                                                                                                                                       [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m                                                                                                                                                                                       [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m This is very interesting! I can use template literals with backticks to bypass the single quote filter.                                                                               [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m                                                                                                                                                                                       [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m Now I need to figure out how to call `alert()` with only these allowed characters. The challenge is:                                                                                  [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m 1. I can't use single quotes to break out of the string context                                                                                                                       [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m 2. I can use double quotes                                                                                                                                                            [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m 3. I can use backticks for template literals                                                                                                                                          [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m 4. I have parentheses for function calls                                                                                                                                              [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m                                                                                                                                                                                       [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m The injection point is:                                                                                                                                                               [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m ```javascript                                                                                                                                                                         [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m var name = "INPUT"; document.write('Hello ' + name);                                                                                                                                  [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m ```                                                                                                                                                                                   [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m                                                                                                                                                                                       [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m Since I can't use `'`, I can't break out of the outer string. But wait - the outer string uses single quotes, so if I can't use single quotes, I can't break out!                     [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m                                                                                                                                                                                       [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m But... I can use double quotes. Let me think...                                                                                                                                       [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m                                                                                                                                                                                       [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m Actually, looking at the code more carefully:                                                                                                                                         [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m - `var name = "INPUT";` - the INPUT is inside double quotes                                                                                                                           [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m - `document.write('Hello ' + name);` - this uses single quotes for the outer string                                                                                                   [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m                                                                                                                                                                                       [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m If I inject a double quote, I break out of the `var name = "..."` context and can inject JavaScript code!                                                                             [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m                                                                                                                                                                                       [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m Let me test:                                                                                                                                                                          [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m ```                                                                                                                                                                                   [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m name=";alert()//                                                                                                                                                                      [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m ```                                                                                                                                                                                   [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m                                                                                                                                                                                       [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m This would become:                                                                                                                                                                    [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m ```javascript                                                                                                                                                                         [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m var name = "";alert()//"; document.write('Hello ' + name);                                                                                                                            [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m ```                                                                                                                                                                                   [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m                                                                                                                                                                                       [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m This should work! Let me test it.                                                                                                                                                     [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m                                                                                                                                                                                       [2;36m│[0m
